<br>
 I am not saying that is how I interpreted it when FV was created. I came here for many things, RP was and is at the top of the list. I RP pretty well for a MAWNAM (middle aged white north american male), but I will never be able to immerse myself to the extent some of you can.<br>
<br>
Recently the massively unrational and poorly thought out arguments that blatently told people to either conform to some people's idea of RP or leave made me angry. I took stands that I believe are true, but not necessarily what I would personally like to see. My analyst side took over and forced me to present arguments in an attempt to balance the sides.<br>
<br>
If you ever have need for a poorly leveling barbarian to take up a sword in your defense we will have a good time. Borm is a very stupid and straight forward warrior. Just do not use too many big words in his presence and you will be alright. (Think large dog). <br>
<br>
I just do not want to see anyone chased off this server because of his/her RP views. If a d00d comes here bashing RP then you will think I am Shintou reborn.<br>
<br>
Borm, stoopid, eer stuped, umm stouped, Dumb warrior. That is it!<br>
<br>
