<br>
Then you said, &quot;I'd like to add that you people should stop trying to say what Verant meant.&quot;<br>
<br>
I'm not the kind of guy who likes to hold people to their exact wording, but this is a pretty blatant contradiction. If you're going to get nasty, at least try to be consistent. And no one here has made personal accusations, Vall, at least that I remember, certainly nothing like &quot;scum of the earth&quot;. Except maybe the people who say &quot;RP nazi&quot;. &quot;Powergamer&quot; and &quot;uberguild&quot; are I think only offensive to people who are ashamed (?) to be in that category. <br>
